      "message": "I love the amount of code that we can remove with this change.\n\nFor the GLSL and Metal code generators, I\u0027d really like it if `writeForStatement` detected a for loop without an initializer or next-expression and emitted `while (test)` instead of `for (;test;)`. I think that dramatically reduces the chance that we find some crazy driver quirk, and also will help readers identify their code post-SkSLification. ",
